<strong>1. A Holistic Approach to Health</strong>

Spas and fitness centers focus on the body, mind, and soul. While fitness prioritize physical activity through gym sessions, yoga, or Pilates,Â  spas complement these efforts by offering therapies like massages, detox treatments, and mindfulness programs.

